            <MadCap:snippetBlock src="../EmptyPageBreakAfter.flsnp" MadCap:conditions="LingoGuides.LingoWhatsNewGuide" />
            <p>When the translator runs the QA&#160;report to check for mismatched punctuation, Lingo recognizes the error and identifies the segment where there is an incorrect period. The translator can then go back and fix the inaccurate punctuation.</p>
